heading_context: If you need help with an existing loan
chunks.html_content:
The Professional and Career Development Loan scheme is now closed for new applications.

If you have an existing loan, it will not be affected.

You’ll still need to repay the loan and any interest, even if you do not complete the course or your course provider goes out of business.

You’ll start repaying the loan (plus interest at a reduced rate) 1 month after leaving your course.

Contact the bank which manages your loan.
chunks.plain_content:
Professional and Career Development Loans
If you need help with an existing loan
The Professional and Career Development Loan scheme is now closed for new applications.
If you have an existing loan, it will not be affected.
You’ll still need to repay the loan and any interest, even if you do not complete the course or your course provider goes out of business.
You’ll start repaying the loan (plus interest at a reduced rate) 1 month after leaving your course.
Contact the bank which manages your loan.
